id":2340544,"uid":28114,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-25T14:23:24.000Z","msg":"Merry Christmas <img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail2_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail2_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail2_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nThank you Australia 🇦🇺"},{"pid":"f07da8a9d0cb3a244efcdfbe7d90eeb7088bdb3d","tid":2340544,"uid":330227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-25T14:23:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e0643af41146781ea6e90c3c5c4ad6ac43008a37","tid":2340544,"uid":27530,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-25T14:24:10.000Z","msg":"「或可」"},{"pid":"d06444cbbb3fc4cebeef2a7e8d3bb2fcf69035e1","tid":2340544,"uid":28114,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-25T14:26:33.000Z","msg":"【獨家】港人申請澳洲新永居簽證　豁免技術簽證一般條件<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.sbs.com.au/language/cantonese/zh-hant/exclusive-good-news-for-hong-kongers-looking-to-apply-for-new-permanent-visa\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.sbs.com.au%2Flanguage%2Fcantonese%2Fzh-hant%2Fexclusive-good-news-for-hong-kongers-looking-to-apply-for-new-permanent-visa&d=E3iW9F3hP8nhDbvOoRyiQIE4T4y%2BYV5jPOnVoTo%2FPYs%3D&h=733f1090\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.sbs.com.au/language/cantonese/zh-hant/exclusive-good-news-for-hong-kongers-looking-to-apply-for-new-permanent-visa</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://sl.sbs.com.au/public/image/file/dc53015b-c8d4-449d-b540-b67d70beda6c/crop/16x9_large\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fsl.sbs.com.au%2Fpublic%2Fimage%2Ffile%2Fdc53015b-c8d4-449d-b540-b67d70beda6c%2Fcrop%2F16x9_large&h=ec665be6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n英國政府公佈更多BN(O)留英計劃細節後一日，澳洲內政部今日（12月24日）亦向本台廣東話組透露港人永久居留簽證計劃的進一步消息。<br />\n<br />\n英國國民（海外）護照「5+1」留英計劃下月31日正式接受港人申請，英國內政部網站昨日公佈最新資訊，釐清了俗稱「太空人計劃」（即家庭成員在不同時間到英國）的具體運作。<br />\n<br />\n根據計劃內容，持有BN(O)的主申請人申請簽證後，會獲得一組獨有編號，其他家庭成員再申請時須填上該編號。如果家庭成員在不同時間赴英，他們未必會在同一時間符合獲得永久居留簽證的資格，可能要再另外申請留英以滿足住滿5年的條件。<br />\n<br />\n在英國昨日公佈留英計劃更多細節後，澳洲內政部今日亦向本台進一步透露港人永居計劃的消息。<br />\n<br />\n澳洲政府今年7月公佈，持有畢業生或臨時技術簽證的港人，可獲延長其臨時簽證5年，並且在5年後（或遍遠地區的留學生住滿3年後）有申請永久居留簽證的「途徑」。<br />\n<br />\n延長臨時簽證的安排已經生效，合資格的港人已獲延長簽證有效期，未來的申請人獲批時亦將直接獲得5年臨時簽證。然而，這些臨時簽證到時後，要如何轉成永居簽證，當局一直未有明確答案。<br />\n<br />\n署理移民部長圖治（Alan Tudge）7月接受澳洲廣播公司專訪時表示：「如果那個人有嚴重的國家安全問題，便會被送走；如果他有品格問題，他們會被送走。所以假設他們沒有那些問題，那他們便合資格得到永久居留權⋯⋯除非他們不符合我剛說的條件，否則他們幾乎可以肯定拿到永久居留簽證。」<br />\n<br />\n本台廣東話組連月來就此問題多番追問內政部，內政部以首個新的永居簽證不會在5年內發出為由，未有明確交代具體要求，只表示新的永居簽證申請人須符合「健康、品格和保安要求」，但拒絕證實它們是否申請永居簽證的全部條件。<br />\n<br />\n本台記者10月23日參加了網上舉行的總理多元文化論壇，希望親身向圖治查詢，惟當日未獲安排發問。<br />\n<br />\n內政部發言人今日回覆本台表示，當日因問題眾多，總理及部長未有一一解答。<br />\n<br />\n不過，發言人進一步透露了申請永居簽證的條件。<br />\n<br />\n他說：「這款永久居留簽證仍在制訂，但合資格的香港護照持有人，將不需要符合其他技術簽證通常要求的額外條件（eligible Hong Kong passport holders will not be required to meet the additional criteria typically required for other skilled visas.）。」<br />\n<br />\n發言人續道：「永久居留簽證選項的更多細節，將在2021年初公佈。」<br />\n<br />\n內政部較早前向本台表示，申請臨時簽證時，須持有香港特區護照才符合延長5年簽證及之後申請永居簽證的資格，若只持有英國國民（海外）護照，則不合資格。"},{"pid":"5c569f6873aa1b7c88115d2f0347d4b5f43d12b0","tid":2340544,"uid":28114,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"e0643af41146781ea6e90c3c5c4ad6ac43008a37","tid":2340544,"uid":27530,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-25T14:24:10.000Z","msg":"「或可」"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-25T14:27:34.000Z","msg":"eligible Hong Kong passport holders will not be required to meet the additional criteria typically required for other skilled visas.<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9352998a72e100dca00bd1536c18f1416fc7b5d2","tid":2340544,"uid":191926,"like":13,"dislike":1,"score":12,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-12-25T14:29:42.000Z","msg":"香港人係國際上算係咁<br />\n<br />\n英國又開<br />\n加拿大又開<br />\n澳洲又開<br />\n美國都會部份開"},{"pid":"80bffef3b449a75a53c7b5b10fa29a5c607abcbb","tid":2340544,"uid":144626,"like":16,"dislike":1,"score":15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-25T14:30:16.000Z","msg":"如果咁搞<br />\n澳洲大可以順水推舟<br />\n收緊支那移民同留學簽證<br />\n將個額俾晒香港人或者多d星馬華人<br />\n就可以補充冇左支那人嘅「損失」"},{"pid":"d6b0e59cf1ab597c02b26bc4ae5c94404192f5bc","tid":2340544,"uid":28114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9352998a72e100dca00bd1536c18f1416fc7b5d2","tid":2340544,"uid":191926,"like":13,"dislike":1,"score":12,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-12-25T14:29:42.000Z","msg":"香港人係國際上算係咁<br />\n<br />\n英國又開<br />\n加拿大又開<br />\n澳洲又開<br />\n美國都會部份開"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-25T14:31:03.000Z","msg":"直頭係仁至義盡<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"75728554f951e1085bc2f80b8796a7477e8dc8df","tid":2340544,"uid":5489,"like":11,"dislike":4,"score":7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-25T14:31:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aaca009b0aac477604d6d847ad594c22947ff30d","tid":2340544,"uid":43731,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"75728554f951e1085bc2f80b8796a7477e8dc8df","tid":2340544,"uid":5489,"like":11,"dislike":4,"score":7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-25T14:31:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"20